i\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"條友真係大陸仔  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15e3b04d41d9541224f80d5c8c6af27c22e15a9","tid":846654,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港若然實現主權獨立後，到底奉行哪一種招兵制度，需由屆時的民選香港國會通過立法程序來決定。筆者相信如果行到這一步的話，屆時在香港民間社會和政界之間必定會有熱烈的討論。無論如何，假設到這一步是相當遙遠的事情，由於假設性太多、不確定因素太多，香港能否建立自己的軍隊、用何種方式招募兵員，充滿著不確定性，這絕不是簡單一句：「香港人若撫心自問，不會有太多人肯讓子女當兵」就可以下定論的。王維基草率地作出如此評論，反映了他對國防政策的陌生，一如他自己所言，他近來日日都花6個鐘頭惡補公共政策。看來王先生也是時候找個熟悉防務議題的顧問，惡補一下國防政策了。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢只係諗緊和平公投路線<br />\n<br />\n但其實仲有第二條路線, 唔係咁樣走既"},{"pid":"4599f7d855b0c0e8e26c8a4d4991c4431b2b4e50","tid":846654,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"搞革命連打手都冇,即係得個講字"},{"pid":"32c7c6e7ed8fe387c3e4da33f9177db916f7715c","tid":846654,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"387242a999b70d17946e3743d483d1b23c0f3cd5","tid":846654,"uid":44105,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"1bf1561ba6c6510666f11209e42581933890d858","tid":846654,"uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":17,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"eb6334438fc309d2888fa24badce963d31ec4897","tid":846654,"uid":44105,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 基拙</span></span><br />\n完來係大陸仔唔撚怪得啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E8BEAFE8AB96E79A84E9AB98E4BD8EE5B1A4E6ACA1_xB7oX_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE8BEAFE8AB96E79A84E9AB98E4BD8EE5B1A4E6ACA1_xB7oX_1200x0.jpg&h=db688e53&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁你真係大陸仔嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c